---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About | River of Life Church" description="Learn about River of Life Church in Henry, IL">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
  </section>

  <section class="content">
    <div class="section">
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>We exist to help people find and follow Jesus. Whether you're exploring faith for the first time or have been walking with God for years, there's a place for you here.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>What to Expect</h2>
      <p>When you visit River of Life, you'll find a friendly, welcoming atmosphere. Our services include contemporary worship music and practical, Bible-based teaching. We have programs for kids and students so the whole family can grow together.</p>
      <p>Come as you are - there's no dress code. We'd love to meet you!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Service Times</h2>
      <div class="service-time">
        <strong>Sunday Morning</strong>
        <span>10:00 AM</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Location</h2>
      <p>Henry, IL</p>
      <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=Henry,IL" target="_blank" class="btn">Get Directions</a>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <h2>Connect With Us</h2>
      <p>Ready to take the next step? Check out our Church Center to find groups, sign up for events, and get connected.</p>
      <a href="https://rolhenry.churchcenter.com/home" target="_blank" class="btn">Visit Church Center</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 4rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
  }

  .section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section h2 {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .section p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .service-time {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    background: var(--color-bg-alt);
    padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .service-time span {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
